  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate whether treatment with the study drug decitabine in
      combination with SHR-1210 is safe and feasible, is more effective than treatment with
      SHR-1210 alone,and reverse the resistance of Anti-PD-1 antibody in patients with HL.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
